<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">read</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token class-name">ByteBuffer</span> dst<span class="token punctuation">)</span> 	从通道读取数据并放到缓冲区中
